{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/2019/08/imgBot-optimize-image-asset-for-github-project/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"dabea80b-787c-5901-a165-36a239c9bea0","html":"<p>我在建<a href=\"https://github.com/BerlinChan/museum\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">旧站博物馆</a>时，旧站内容中有不少图片，数量巨大不便于逐个处理，部分人工筛选和压缩后，闲逛 <a href=\"https://github.com/marketplace\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Github Marketplace</a> 时看到了这个 <a href=\"https://github.com/marketplace/imgbot\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">ImgBot</a>。</p>\n<!-- endExcerpt -->\n<p>⚠️ 开始之前值得一提的是，使用在线工具存在安全风险。处理包含敏感内容的图片，应使用本地工具。</p>\n<h2 id=\"介绍-imgbot\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E4%BB%8B%E7%BB%8D-imgbot\" aria-label=\"介绍 imgbot permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>介绍 ImgBot</h2>\n<p>官方介绍翻译：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>ImgBot 是一个为你节省时间优化图片的机器人。优化图片意味着不牺牲图片质量和更小的文件大小。\n安装后不久，你会收到一个优化图片的 pull request。合并这个 pull request 就行了！Imgbot 会伴随你的工作，保持图片的优化。\nImgBot 默认使用无损压缩。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"使用-imgbot\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-imgbot\" aria-label=\"使用 imgbot permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>使用 ImgBot</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/marketplace/imgbot\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">ImgBot</a> 对开源项目是免费的，点最下面的安装按钮然后选择要安装的项目就完成，太简单就不放图了，过几分钟我就收到优化图片后的 pull request，如下：</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 755px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/191b1e9bd4cebce5bc819fe2e22688aa/92579/pull-request-from-ImgBot.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 77.36842105263158%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/191b1e9bd4cebce5bc819fe2e22688aa/5ed05/pull-request-from-ImgBot.webp 190w,\n/static/191b1e9bd4cebce5bc819fe2e22688aa/9d76b/pull-request-from-ImgBot.webp 380w,\n/static/191b1e9bd4cebce5bc819fe2e22688aa/0f085/pull-request-from-ImgBot.webp 755w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 755px) 100vw, 755px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/191b1e9bd4cebce5bc819fe2e22688aa/89129/pull-request-from-ImgBot.jpg 190w,\n/static/191b1e9bd4cebce5bc819fe2e22688aa/0036d/pull-request-from-ImgBot.jpg 380w,\n/static/191b1e9bd4cebce5bc819fe2e22688aa/92579/pull-request-from-ImgBot.jpg 755w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 755px) 100vw, 755px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/191b1e9bd4cebce5bc819fe2e22688aa/92579/pull-request-from-ImgBot.jpg\"\n            alt=\"pull-request-from-ImgBot\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>被优化图片的报告可见，png 图片文件大小最高被优化掉88.43%，很可观的数字！总体被优化掉4.48%。</p>\n<p>ImgBot 默认是无损压缩的，可以按需进行<a href=\"https://imgbot.net/docs/#configuration\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">配置</a>为有损压缩，对文件大小进一步压榨。</p>\n<p>配置方法是在根目录放置文件 <code class=\"language-text\">.imgbotconfig</code>,内容如下</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"aggressiveCompression\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"true\"</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 使用有损压缩 true|false</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>还有更多配置项，完整说明请见<a href=\"https://imgbot.net/docs/#configuration\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">官方文档</a></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"schedule\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"daily\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 执行周期 daily|weekly|monthly</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"ignoredFiles\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"*.jpg\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>                   <span class=\"token comment\">// ignore by extension</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"image1.png\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>              <span class=\"token comment\">// ignore by filename</span>\n        <span class=\"token string\">\"public/special_images/*\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// ignore by folderpath</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"aggressiveCompression\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"true\"</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 使用有损压缩 true|false</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"另外推荐-tinypng\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%8F%A6%E5%A4%96%E6%8E%A8%E8%8D%90-tinypng\" aria-label=\"另外推荐 tinypng permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>另外推荐 TinyPNG</h2>\n<p>后来我将经 ImgBot 无损压缩优化后的图片放到 <a href=\"https://tinypng.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">TinyPNG</a> 中，竟然还能压榨掉很多字节，因为 TinyPNG 采用的是<strong>有损压缩</strong>，官方说明翻译：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>TinyPNG 采用智能有损压缩技术来优化 PNG 文件大小。有选择地减少图片中的颜色，用更少的字节数存储。图片损失几乎不可见，但文件大小有很大改善。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>TingPNG 是个不错的另外选择，他还提供压缩、智能裁剪的 API 用于批量处理。不过 ImgBot 也可以配置为有损压缩的，对于图片多的还是配置 ImgBot 简单又省事。</p>\n<h2 id=\"更新-2025-10-30\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0-2025-10-30\" aria-label=\"更新 2025 10 30 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>更新 2025-10-30</h2>\n<p>TinyPNG 的免费服务最大支持 5MB 文件的处理，对于更大文件的支持需要订阅 Web Pro。网友 Ana 推荐另一款在线图片压缩工具 <a href=\"https://www.websiteplanet.com/webtools/imagecompressor/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">imagecompressor</a>，其支持最大 50MB 文件的处理。经实测，压缩一张 49.5MB 的 PNG 是没有问题的。</p>","excerpt":"我在建旧站博物馆时，旧站内容中有不少图片，数量巨大不便于逐个处理，部分人工筛选和压缩后，闲逛 Github Marketplace 时看到了这个 ImgBot。","fields":{"slug":"/2019/08/imgBot-optimize-image-asset-for-github-project","categorySlugs":["/category/前端/"],"tagSlugs":["/tag/性能/","/tag/github/"]},"frontmatter":{"title":"使用 ImgBot 自动为 Github 项目优化图片","date":"2019-08-11T10:46:37.121Z","categories":["前端"],"description":"用 Github Pages 做 blog 时，经常会插入很多图片，利用 ImgBot 可以自动为我们优化图片大小，加快图片加载","tags":["性能","Github"],"slug":"/2019/08/imgBot-optimize-image-asset-for-github-project","featured_media":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"fixed","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/a1bfccc03618cdd057837edaf381ee4b/ed3fb/github-imgbot.png","srcSet":"/static/a1bfccc03618cdd057837edaf381ee4b/ed3fb/github-imgbot.png 800w","sizes":"800px"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/a1bfccc03618cdd057837edaf381ee4b/e7773/github-imgbot.webp 800w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"800px"}]},"width":800,"height":400}}}}},"prevPost":{"fields":{"slug":"/2019/05/mothers-day-yichang"},"frontmatter":{"title":"母亲节回宜昌"}},"nextPost":{"fields":{"slug":"/2019/08/migrate-from-wordpress-to-gatsby"},"frontmatter":{"title":"博客从 Wordpress 迁移到 Gatsby"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2019/08/imgBot-optimize-image-asset-for-github-project","prevPostSlug":"/2019/0